hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: An estate agents texhealthct.org Tom told me he hated school so I asked him, was there anything the teachers could do for his behaviour to improve? ‘Don’t put me in lessons,’ he said. ‘Give me a work placement, give me some work to do.’ When I asked Tom what his ambition was he said it was to be a builder or a joiner but, heartbreakingly, he has already written off his chances. ‘I won’t get into college because of my behaviour record,’ he said flatly, ‘so I will try to get into the Army.’
